      "text": [
        " أَبُو جَعْفَرٍ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : «بُنِيَ اَلْإِسْلاَمُ عَلَى خَمْسَةِ أَشْيَاءَ عَلَى اَلصَّلاَةِ وَ اَلزَّكَاةِ وَ اَلْحَجِّ وَ اَلصَّوْمِ وَ اَلْوَلاَيَةِ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1770 - Abu Ja’far (Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as)) said:\n\"Islam is built upon five things: prayer, almsgiving, pilgrimage, fasting, and wilayah (divinely appointed leadership).\""
        ]
      }
